2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a deep reinforcement learning algorithm for solving the scheduling problem. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with estimating the states of multiple remote, dynamic processes. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is a possible category as the paper deals with scheduling multiple sensors for monitoring purposes. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper uses a machine learning algorithm for solving the scheduling problem.
